rows.label: tlk41200141_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Claudio-san gave me a Gulan
Woodwing as a gift.

rows.label: tlk41200141_03_msg0002
rows.name:
He bought it for me so it would remind
me of home.

rows.label: tlk41200141_03_msg0003
rows.name:
It's got this feathery pattern on it
that's the same as my old clothes.
It made me so happy...

rows.label: tlk41200141_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I think I'm gonna be a dressmaker
when I grow up.

rows.label: tlk41200141_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Maybe someday, I'll be able to cheer
up these people the same way they
cheered me up!
